function GR(T);if file_exists("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/"..T) == "NO" then;toast("Not "..T);else;end;local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/"..T.."",1), "rb"); local nameY = f:read("*all"); f:close();return nameY;end;--function GR(T)


function fixGsub()
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/1.ACC/ACC.txt", "rb"); local Z1 = f:read("*all"); f:close();			
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/MAX2020/1.ACC/ACC.txt", "rb"); local Z2 = f:read("*all"); f:close();			
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/1.ACC/LIVE.txt", "rb"); local Z3 = f:read("*all"); f:close();			
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/MAX2020/1.ACC/LIVE.txt", "rb"); local Z4 = f:read("*all"); f:close();			
usleep(100000);
Z1 = string.gsub(Z1, " ", "");Z2 = string.gsub(Z2, " ", "");Z3 = string.gsub(Z3, " ", "");Z4 = string.gsub(Z4, " ", "")
usleep(100000);
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/1.ACC/ACC.txt", "w");f:write(Z1);f:close() 
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/MAX2020/1.ACC/ACC.txt", "w");f:write(Z2);f:close() 
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/1.ACC/LIVE.txt", "w");f:write(Z3);f:close() 
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/MAX2020/1.ACC/LIVE.txt", "w");f:write(Z4);f:close();usleep(100000); 
end;--function fixGsub()

end;--function PC2MAX()

function split(s, d)
    r = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(r, m);
    end
    return r;
end

		usleep(200000)
	end;
usleep(1000000);
end;--hashtag

function GetNDUPDATE(RJ)
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/NDUPDATE", "rb"); local content = f:read("*all"); f:close(); 	
local LineInUIDfile = 1  -----none of set value--Get line
local ColumeX1 = 1 -----none of set value--get colummn 1
local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2
local ColumeX3 = 3 -----none of set value--get colummn 3
local ColumeX4 = 4 -----none of set value--get colummn 4
function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do
	local line = v
	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')
--toast(''..UID_PASS[ColumeX1]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX2]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX3]..'', 2)
		copyText("Update")
	local UIDX = UID_PASS[RJ] --input Col
	--local PassX = UID_PASS[2]
	--local Code2FAX = UID_PASS[4]
UID = string.gsub(UIDX, " ", "");copyText(UIDX)
		
		end;--end call value	
					
end;--GetNDUPDATE(RJ)

function clBackup()
local date = os.date("%d");
if tonumber(date) % 10 == 0  then 
--if tonumber(date) % 5 == 0 or tonumber(date) < 10 then 		
io.popen("rm -f /var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../Backup/*");
io.popen("rm -f /var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/MAX2020/1.ACC/BACKUP/*");
io.popen("rm -f /var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/1.ACC/BACKUP/*");
else;end;	
end;

	function getSZ()
preX = string.sub(getSN(), 1, 5)
subX = string.sub(getSN(), -5, -1)
--toast(preX.."***"..subX);
getSZ = preX.."***"..subX
	return getSZ
	end;--



function AlrtBnk()
TimeX = tonumber(os.date("%d"))
if TimeX < 10 then;
	alert("H√¥m nay l√† ng√†y "..TimeX.." c·ªßa th√°ng!\nN√™n ph√≠ k√≠ch l√† 150K/m√°y\n\nK√≠ch sau ng√†y 10:\n100K/m√°y")		
elseif TimeX >= 10 and TimeX < 20 then

function file_exists(name)
io.popen('activator send switch-off.com.a3tweaks.switch.wifi')	
   local f=io.open(name,"r")
	NO = "NO"
  -- if f~=nil then io.close(f) return true else return false end
	if f~=nil then io.close(f) 
		OK = "OK"
		
		return OK 
	else 
		OK = "NO"
		return OK
	end
end

function r(name,input1)
	if name == nil and input1 == nil then
		root = "/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/"
	elseif input1 == nil then
	local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/IDapp.txt", "rb"); local IDapp = f:read("*all"); f:close(); --usleep(50000);
		log("--"..IDapp..name)
		
for i, v in pairs(findImage("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/imagesss/Skip.BiMess.png", 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;
for i, v in pairs(findImage("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/imagesss/Skip.iMess.png", 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;
	tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(500000);end;end;usleep(50000)
		
	root = "/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/imagesss/"..name..".png"
	elseif input1 == 2 then
		root = "/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/"..name..""
	else
		root = "/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/"..name..""
		end;--if name == nil then
	return root
	end;
function rx(name,input1)
	if name == nil and input1 == nil then
		root = "/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/"
	elseif input1 == 1 then
		root = name
		else;end;
	return root
	end;
function count(name)
local f=io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/"..name..".txt","r");
if f~=nil then io.close(f) 
 sodong = 0
  for i in io.lines("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/"..name..".txt") do
    sodong = sodong + 1
  end 
--toast(sodong)
return sodong
else 
return toast("file kh√¥ng t·ªìn t·∫°i") end 
end

function c0unt(file)
local f=io.open(file,"r");
if f~=nil then io.close(f) 
 sodong = 0
  for i in io.lines(file) do
    sodong = sodong + 1
  end 
--toast(sodong)
return sodong
else 
return toast("file kh√¥ng t·ªìn t·∫°i") end 
end

local now = os.time();local locations;repeat;
--io.popen('activator send switch-off.com.a3tweaks.switch.wifi');	usleep(200000)		
--for i, v in pairs(findImage("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/imagesss/Skip.BiMess.png", 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;--usleep(50000)
--for i, v in pairs(findImage("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/imagesss/Skip.iMess.png", 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;
	--tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(500000);end;end;		
		local locations = findImage(r(name), 1, 0.98, region, false);usleep(300000);until(#locations > 0) or os.time()-now>=tonumber(input);usleep(50000)
end;

function toastcfT(time)
	--local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/cf",1), "rb"); local cf = f:read("*all"); f:close();

inputText("\b\b\b\b\b\b\b\b\b\b\b"); usleep(500000);		
tap(v[1], v[2]);  usleep(300000);
--[[

touchUp(2, v[1], v[2]);]]
usleep(1000000)

tap(v[1], v[2]);  usleep(1500000);         end;---fky2.png

	end;---fky1.png 
	usleep(1000000); 
end;--function fky1()

function Get2FATT() 
io.popen('activator send switch-off.com.a3tweaks.switch.wifi');usleep(150000);
--local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input1", "rb"); local input1 = f:read("*all"); 

	--local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/2FA.txt", "rb"); local input1 = f:read("*all"); 
	CodeZ = clipText()

    local http = require("socket.http")
local body, code = http.request("http://103.145.252.81:6868/Api/GetAuthyCode?Key="..CodeZ.."")
	--usleep(3000000);

	if string.len(body) < 10 then --Get2FAX(CodeX);usleep(3000000);
		toast(body,5);copyText(body)
else;
toast("Server2FA Error");--Get2FAfAPP();usleep(300000);--copyText("Server2FA Error");		
end;	
end;

			 NetCheck();usleep(100000);
		     if NetOK == "OK" then
		        local http = require("socket.http");local body, code = http.request("http://2fa.live/tok/"..Code2FAT.."")
	            if body == nil then ;toast(body);log("nil "..body);elseif string.len(body) < 20 then;
          pa1 = string.sub(body, -8, -3);usleep(500000);toast(pa1);log("get2FA:"..body);copyText(pa1);usleep(500000);break; --XCVKLXVXCJKLV --> CJKLV

             else;toast(body);log("not nil, but fail"..body);end;
			else;end;--if NetOK == "OK" then
	usleep(300000);
end;--for RZ = 1, 5 do
		if string.len(pa1) ~= 6 then
			Get2FAfAPP();
		--Get2FATT();

end;--function get2FANOTAPP()

function inputSTT()
io.popen('activator send switch-off.com.a3tweaks.switch.wifi');usleep(500000);

 file = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/ContentX.txt",1), "w");file:write("0");file:close()

local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/NSTT", "rb"); local NumberContentSale = f:read("*all"); f:close(); usleep(300000);
if tonumber(NumberContentSale) < 150 then toast("                C·∫¢NH B√ÅO\n\nB·∫°n ƒëang c√≥ ch·ªâ "..(tonumber(NumberContentSale)-1).." b√†i\nB√†i qu√° √≠t,kh√¥ng an to√†n\nN√™n t·ª´ 150 b√†i tr·ªü l√™n\n\nTh∆∞ M·ª•c c·∫ßn s·ª≠a: 2.UpSTT");else;end;
--random ContentX
    --=========================================================================
for RXp = 1, (os.date ("%H"))+(os.date ("%M"))+(os.date ("%S")) do;RA = math.random(2,tonumber(NumberContentSale));usleep(5000);copyText(RA);toast("MAX2020Pre's random loading...\n                      "..RA.."/"..RXp);end;
--for rScrollIn = 1, RAl do ScrollInListShare();usleep(50000);toast(rScrollIn.."/"..RAl);end;usleep(500000);
ContentX = RA;usleep(100000);
file = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/ContentY.txt",1), "w"); file:write(""..ContentX.."");file:close();usleep(100000);	
	
    --=========================================================================
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/ContentY.txt",1), "rb"); local ContentX = f:read("*all"); f:close(); usleep(300000);
toast(ContentX);log("UpSTT: "..ContentX.."");
	--===============================================================
if file_exists("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/2.UpSTT/"..ContentX..".txt") == "OK" then
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/2.UpSTT/"..ContentX..".txt", "rb"); local content = f:read("*all"); f:close(); copyText(content);usleep(500000);
else;
toast("B√†i b·∫°n ch√©p b·ªã thi·∫øu b√†i s·ªë "..ContentX..".txt\n H√£y t·∫°o th√™m trong th∆∞ m·ª•c 2.UpSTT",1000000);
log("\n==============\nB√†i b·∫°n ch√©p b·ªã thi·∫øu b√†i s·ªë "..ContentX..".txt\n H√£y t·∫°o th√™m trong th∆∞ m·ª•c 2.UpSTT");

end;--function inputSTT()

}

function FrankyNouva(namecall,input1,input2,input3,input4,input5,input6,input7);
	namecall= tostring(namecall)
	input1= tostring(input1)
	input2= tostring(input2)
	input3= tostring(input3)
	input4= tostring(input4)
	input5= tostring(input5)
	input6= tostring(input6)
	input6= tostring(input7)
     local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/ate", "w");f:write(namecall);f:close();
	if input1 == nil then local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input1", "w");f:write("0");f:close();
		else local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input1", "w");f:write(tostring(input1));f:close(); end
	if input2 == nil then local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input2", "w");f:write("0");f:close();
		else local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input2", "w");f:write(tostring(input2));f:close(); end
	if input3 == nil then local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input3", "w");f:write("0");f:close();
		else local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input3", "w");f:write(tostring(input3));f:close(); end
	if input4 == nil then local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input4", "w");f:write("0");f:close();
		else local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input4", "w");f:write(tostring(input4));f:close(); end
	if input5 == nil then local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input5", "w");f:write("0");f:close();
		else local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input5", "w");f:write(tostring(input5));f:close(); end
	if input6 == nil then local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input6", "w");f:write("0");f:close();
		else local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input6", "w");f:write(tostring(input6));f:close(); end
	if input6 == nil then local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input7", "w");f:write("0");f:close();
		else local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../temmp/input7", "w");f:write(tostring(input6));f:close(); end

	usleep(100000)
end;

function dlt()	
local body, code = require("socket.http").request('https://github.com/CrazyMKTFarmer/CrazyMKTFarmer.github.io/raw/master/code/RX.zip')
if code == 200 then;
io.popen("rm -f /var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Library/RX.zip");usleep(100000);	
local f = assert(io.open('/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Library/RX.zip', 'wb')) ;f:write(body);f:close();usleep(100000);else;end;
end;--function dlt()

function fixSkipEditProfile()
--ot("ChangeBio.BEdit",3) ;

	tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(500000);

	tap(v[1]-5+math.random(5,10), v[2]+math.random(1,5));usleep(500000);end;end;--ChangeBio.BEdit--ChangeBio.BEditStop
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("Autologin.savelogin"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;	
tap(math.random(410,650), v[2]-math.random(1,10)); usleep(math.random(300000,800000));end;--Autologin.savelogin.png
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("Autologin.skip"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;	
 tap(v[1]+math.random(1,5), v[2]+math.random(1,5)); usleep(math.random(300000,800000));end;--Autologin.skip.png	
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("Autologin.skip"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;
 tap(v[1]+math.random(1,5), v[2]+math.random(1,5)); usleep(math.random(300000,800000));end;--Autologin.skip.png
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("Autologin.skip"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;	
 tap(v[1]+math.random(1,5), v[2]+math.random(1,5)); usleep(math.random(300000,800000));end;--Autologin.skip.png	
end;--function fixSkipEditProfile()

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end

        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function checklogin()

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end

--========================================================================================================				
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/LIVE.txt",1), "rb"); local content = f:read("*all"); f:close(); 	
local LineInUIDfile = ranCheck  -----none of set value--Get line
local ColumeX1 = 1 -----none of set value--get colummn 1
local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2
local ColumeX3 = 3 -----none of set value--get colummn 3
local ColumeX4 = 4 -----none of set value--get colummn 4
function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do
	local line = v
	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')
--toast(''..UID_PASS[ColumeX1]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX2]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX3]..'', 2)
	local UIDX = UID_PASS[1]
	local PassX = UID_PASS[2]
	local Code2FAX = UID_PASS[4]
UID = string.gsub(UIDX, " ", "");copyText(UID)				
				
		end;--end call value	
					
end;--rU()

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]

	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]

		end;

local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2
local ColumeX3 = 3 -----none of set value--get colummn 3
local ColumeX4 = 4 -----none of set value--get colummn 4
function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do
	local line = v
	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')
--toast(''..UID_PASS[ColumeX1]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX2]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX3]..'', 2)
	local UIDX = UID_PASS[1]
	local PassX = UID_PASS[2]
	local Code2FAX = UID_PASS[4]
	copyText(UIDX); --toast(UIDX)
	LinkX = UIDX			
		end;--end call value	
					
end;--rUT()

function Ract()
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("ReactWatch.Like"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;--tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(300000)       
touchDown(3, v[1], v[2]);
usleep(617166.46);
touchUp(3, v[1], v[2]);
usleep(117166.46);
end;--LikeNewsfeed.like
usleep(300000) 	
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("ReactWatch.Like1"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;--tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(300000)       
touchDown(3, v[1], v[2]);
usleep(617166.46);
touchUp(3, v[1], v[2]);
usleep(117166.46);
end;--LikeNewsfeed.like	
	
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("LikeNewsfeed.react"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;--tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(300000) 
	RegionReactX = {100-math.random(5,20),200-math.random(5,20),300-math.random(5,20),400-math.random(5,20)};RegionReactX = RegionReactX[math.random(1, #RegionReactX)] 
	RegionReactY = {v[2]-math.random(5,45)};RegionReactY = RegionReactY[math.random(1, #RegionReactY)]; usleep(100000);      
 tap(RegionReactX, RegionReactY);     usleep(500000); 
end;--LikeNewsfeed.react.png

end;--function Ract()

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
			
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do
	local line = v
	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')
--toast(''..UID_PASS[ColumeX1]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX2]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX3]..'', 2)
	local UIDX = UID_PASS[1]
	local PassX = UID_PASS[2]
	local Code2FAX = UID_PASS[4]
	--copyText(UIDX); --toast(UIDX)
UID = string.gsub(UIDX, " ", "")				
copyText(UID)				
		end;--end call value	
					
end;--rU()

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
			
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do
	local line = v
	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')
--toast(''..UID_PASS[ColumeX1]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX2]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX3]..'', 2)
	local UIDX = UID_PASS[1]
	local PassX = UID_PASS[2]
	local Code2FAX = UID_PASS[4]
	--copyText(UIDX); --toast(UIDX)
UID = string.gsub(UIDX, " ", "")				
copyText(UID)				
		end;--end call value

function rChmB()
--==========================================================					
usleep(100000)

end;--Autologin.findconnect.png
--===============================================================================
usleep(100000)
--===============================================================================

lppscrX  = math.random(1,25)
rCh = math.random(1,6)
toast(lppscrX.."/"..(lppscrX-1)*6+rCh,lppscrX*2)

--if lppscrX == 1 then
	--else
	
	for lppscrX = 1,lppscrX-1 do;ScrollinStory();usleep(500000);end;--lppscrX

function rChmB()
--==========================================================					
usleep(100000)
--==========================================================

 tap(v[1]+math.random(1,5), v[2]+math.random(1,5)); usleep(1000000); ;end;--Autologin.OKfindconnect.png 
end;--Autologin.findconnect.png
--===============================================================================
usleep(100000)

lppscrX  = math.random(1,25)

rCh = math.random(1,6)

toast(lppscrX.."/"..(lppscrX-1)*6+rCh,lppscrX*2)

--if lppscrX < 3 then
	--else

--end;--check lppscrX

	end;--rCh

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]

local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
			
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do
	local line = v
	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')
--toast(''..UID_PASS[ColumeX1]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX2]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX3]..'', 2)
	local UIDX = UID_PASS[1]
	local PassX = UID_PASS[2]
	local Code2FAX = UID_PASS[4]
	--copyText(UIDX); --toast(UIDX)
UID = string.gsub(UIDX, " ", "")				
copyText(UID)				
		end;--end call value

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)

function fixdraf()
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("PostSTT.color.fix1"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;
	tap(v[1], v[2]);     usleep(math.random(800000,1000000));end;
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("PostSTT.color.fix2"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;
	tap(v[1], v[2]);     usleep(math.random(800000,1000000));end;
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("PostSTT.color.fix3"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;
	tap(v[1], v[2]);     usleep(math.random(800000,1000000));end;
end;

		end;

local ColumeX1 = 1 -----none of set value--get colummn 1
local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2
local ColumeX3 = 3 -----none of set value--get colummn 3
local ColumeX4 = 4 -----none of set value--get colummn 4
function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do
	local line = v
	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')
--toast(''..UID_PASS[ColumeX1]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX2]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX3]..'', 2)
	local UIDX = UID_PASS[1]
	local PassX = UID_PASS[2]
	local Code2FAX = UID_PASS[4]
	copyText(UIDX); toast(UIDX)
				
		end;--end call value

	else
inputText(clipText());usleep(500000);	
	end;
	
end;--rU()

    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end

        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function tapShare()
	
	ShareBtn = findColors({{1603570,0,0}, {1603570,11,9}, {1603570,5,17}, {1603570,18,-3}, {1603570,19,15}, {1603570,28,13}, {1603570,36,13}, {1603570,46,12}, {1603570,54,4}, {1603570,54,16}, {1603570,75,7}, {1603570,70,16}}, 0, nil);
for i, v in pairs(ShareBtn) do; toast("ShareBtnOK")
	tap(v[1] + math.random(2,10), v[2]+ math.random(2,10));
	ShareBtnOK = "1"
		usleep(math.random(2000000,3000000));
	break;end;
end;--function tapShare()

function rU()
--ranCheck = math.random(2,c0unt(r("/MAX2020/NDSharePost.txt",1))-1) 	
		if c0unt("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/NDSharePost.txt") < 3 then			
			toast("                        C·∫¢NH B√ÅO\n\nTh√™m qu√° √≠t d√≤ng (d∆∞·ªõi < 10 d·ªÖ bay acc)\nTh√≠ch LI·ªÄU c√≥ th·ªÉ nh√¢n l√™n nhi·ªÅu d√≤ng\nB·ªÅn v·ªØng, l√¢u d√†i th√¨ t·ªëi thi·ªÉu 20 d√≤ng\n\nƒê√¢y l√† file c·∫ßn s·ª≠a: NDSharePost.txt",5);	log("B·∫°n th√™m qu√° √≠t d√≤ng NDSharePost.txt");
ranCheck = 2			
		else;
ranCheck = math.random(2,c0unt("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/NDSharePost.txt")-1);	 	
		end;			
			
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/NDSharePost.txt", "rb"); local content = f:read("*all"); f:close(); 	
local LineInUIDfile = ranCheck  -----none of set value--Get line
local ColumeX1 = 1 -----none of set value--get colummn 1
local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2
local ColumeX3 = 3 -----none of set value--get colummn 3
local ColumeX4 = 4 -----none of set value--get colummn 4
function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do
	local line = v
	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')
--toast(''..UID_PASS[ColumeX1]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX2]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX3]..'', 2)
	local UIDX = UID_PASS[1]
	local PassX = UID_PASS[2]
	local Code2FAX = UID_PASS[4]
	copyText(UIDX); --toast(UIDX)
	NDX = UIDX			
		end;--end call value	
					
end;--rU()

		end;

local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end

function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]

function rU()
--ranCheck = math.random(2,c0unt(r("/MAX2020/NDShareLink.txt",1))-1) 	
		if c0unt("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/NDShareLink.txt") < 3 then			
			toast("                        C·∫¢NH B√ÅO\n\nTh√™m qu√° √≠t d√≤ng (d∆∞·ªõi < 10 d·ªÖ bay acc)\nTh√≠ch LI·ªÄU c√≥ th·ªÉ nh√¢n l√™n nhi·ªÅu d√≤ng\nB·ªÅn v·ªØng, l√¢u d√†i th√¨ t·ªëi thi·ªÉu 20 d√≤ng\n\nƒê√¢y l√† file c·∫ßn s·ª≠a: NDShareLink.txt",5);	log("B·∫°n th√™m qu√° √≠t d√≤ng NDShareLink.txt");
ranCheck = 2			
		else;
ranCheck = math.random(2,c0unt("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/NDShareLink.txt")-1);	 	
		end;			
			
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/NDShareLink.txt", "rb"); local content = f:read("*all"); f:close(); 	
local LineInUIDfile = ranCheck  -----none of set value--Get line
local ColumeX1 = 1 -----none of set value--get colummn 1
local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2
local ColumeX3 = 3 -----none of set value--get colummn 3
local ColumeX4 = 4 -----none of set value--get colummn 4
function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do
	local line = v
	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')
--toast(''..UID_PASS[ColumeX1]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX2]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX3]..'', 2)
	local UIDX = UID_PASS[1]
	local PassX = UID_PASS[2]
	local Code2FAX = UID_PASS[4]
	copyText(UIDX); --toast(UIDX)
				
		end;--end call value	
					
end;--rU()

local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')

copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')

function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')

function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function CMTMediachoose()

local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/H63H",1), "rb"); local H63H = f:read("*all"); f:close(); 
	
    if H63H == "1" then
	A1 = "Album1AA"
	A2 = "Album1AA"			
elseif H63H== "2" then		
	A1 = "Album2BB"	
	A2 = "Album2BB"			
elseif H63H== "3" then		
	A1 = "Album3CC"
	A2 = "Album3CC"
elseif H63H== "4" then		
	A1 = "Album4DD"	
	A2 = "Album4DD"
elseif H63H== "5" then		
	A1 = "Album5EE"	
	A2 = "Album5EE"	
elseif H63H== "6" then		
	A1 = "Album6FF"
	A2 = "Album6FF"	
elseif H63H== "7" then		
	A1 = "Album7GG"	
	A2 = "Album7GG"			
elseif H63H== "8" then		
	A1 = "Album8HH"	
	A2 = "Album8HH"			
elseif H63H== "9" then		
	A1 = "Album9II"	
	A2 = "Album9II"			
elseif H63H== "10" then			
	A1 = "Album10JJ"	
	A2 = "Album10JJ"				
	else
   A1 = "Album3CC"
  A2 = "Album3CC"
	end;

function rChooseImage()

--top()
touchDown(4, 305.87, 10.63);
usleep(100098.54);
touchUp(4, 305.87, 10.63);
usleep(1000000);

	--=========================================================================
for RXp = 1, (os.date ("%H"))+(os.date ("%M"))+(os.date ("%S")) do;RA = math.random(2,30);usleep(5000);toast("MAX2020Pre's random loading...\n                      "..RA.."/"..RXp);end;

function CMTgif()

if tonumber(A63A) == 0 then
		else;

hashtagA = hashtagA[math.random(1,#hashtagA)];usleep(100000);	
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.gif"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;

		end;--CMTPost.gif
	end;--if tonumber(A63A) == 0 then
end;--function CMTgif()

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]			
			inputText(LineX);usleep(500000);	
		
					
end;--rU()
rU();usleep(500000);
CMTmedia4txt();usleep(500000);
		end;--if tonumber(D63D) == 0 then
end;--function CMTtxt4Media()

		else;

    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end

function MainfunctionCMTGroup()	
  function Sencmt()
	ot("CMTPost.Sendcmt",3);for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.Sendcmt"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;
   tap(v[1]+math.random(1,10) , v[2]+math.random(1,5));usleep(500000);
   CMTOK = "1";usleep(2500000);		
							
	--=======================================================================================						
if CMTmedia == "1" then
ot("CMTPost.Media.posting",5);for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.Media.posting"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;--tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(300000)  
						--tap(v[1], v[2]);     usleep(math.random(1000000,1200000)); 
toast("wait for uploading...",10); usleep(2000000);	
ot("CMTPost.Media.justnow",30);for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.Media.justnow"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;--tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(300000)  
toast("upload video done..."); usleep(2000000)
			
	end;--CMTPost.Media.justnow
	end;--CMTPost.Media.posting
		else;end;--if CMTmedia == "1" then
		CMTmedia = "0"	
	--=======================================================================================
													
							
   end;--CMTPost.Sendcmt	
  end;--function Sencmt()

for rCMT = 1,math.random(1,6) do rAXX = math.random(1,5);usleep(100000);end;
	toast("type cmt is "..rAXX.."",20)
	if rAXX == 1 then

function rUCMTProfileGetUID()

if file_exists("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/D64D") == "OK" then;else;
file = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/D64D",1), "w"); file:write("0");file:close();usleep(100000);end;	
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/D64D",1), "rb"); local D64D = f:read("*all"); f:close(); usleep(100000);
		
--ranCheck = math.random(2,c0unt(r("MAX2020/CMTProfile(UID).txt",1))-1) 	 			
		if c0unt("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/CMTProfile(UID).txt") < 3 then			
			--toast("H√£y th√™m nhi·ªÅu UID h∆°n\nB·∫°n c√≥ qu√° √≠t cmt trong CMTProfile(UID).txt",10);	log("B·∫°n c√≤n qu√° √≠t UID trong CMTProfile(UID).txt")	; 
ranCheck = 2			
		else;
ranCheck = math.random(2,c0unt("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/CMTProfile(UID).txt")-1) 				
		end;
--========================================================================================================
if file_exists("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/OCMTProfileUID.txt") == "OK" then;else;
file = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/OCMTProfileUID.txt",1), "w"); file:write("2");file:close();usleep(100000);end;															
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/OCMTProfileUID.txt",1), "rb"); local CMTProfileUID = f:read("*all"); f:close(); usleep(100000);
OCMTProfileUIDX = tonumber(CMTProfileUID) + 1
file = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/OCMTProfileUID.txt",1), "w"); file:write(OCMTProfileUIDX);file:close();usleep(100000);			
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/OCMTProfileUID.txt",1), "rb"); local OCMTProfileUID = f:read("*all"); f:close(); usleep(100000);

if tonumber(OCMTProfileUID) > c0unt("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/CMTProfile(UID).txt") then
file = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/OCMTProfileUID.txt",1), "w"); file:write("2");file:close();usleep(100000);					
else;end;--if tonumber(OCMTGroup) > c0unt(r("MAX2020/CMTProfile(UID).txt",1)) then

local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/OCMTProfileUID.txt",1), "rb"); OCMTProfileUID = f:read("*all"); f:close(); usleep(100000);
ranCheck = tonumber(OCMTProfileUID)
--========================================================================================================	
if ranCheck == 1 then ranCheck = 2 else;end;		
local f = io.open("/var/mobile/Media/general_storage/MAX2020/CMTProfile(UID).txt", "rb"); local content = f:read("*all"); f:close(); 	
local LineInUIDfile = ranCheck  -----none of set value--Get line
local ColumeX1 = 1 -----none of set value--get colummn 1
local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2
local ColumeX3 = 3 -----none of set value--get colummn 3
local ColumeX4 = 4 -----none of set value--get colummn 4
function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]			
UID = string.gsub(LineX, " ", "");usleep(100000);				
copyText(UID)

end;--function rUCMTProfileGetUID()

function CMTMediachoose()
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/H64H",1), "rb"); local H64H = f:read("*all"); f:close(); 
	
    if H64H == "1" then
	A1 = "Album1AA"
	A2 = "Album1AA"			
elseif H64H== "2" then		
	A1 = "Album2BB"	
	A2 = "Album2BB"			
elseif H64H== "3" then		
	A1 = "Album3CC"
	A2 = "Album3CC"
elseif H64H== "4" then		
	A1 = "Album4DD"	
	A2 = "Album4DD"
elseif H64H== "5" then		
	A1 = "Album5EE"	
	A2 = "Album5EE"	
elseif H64H== "6" then		
	A1 = "Album6FF"
	A2 = "Album6FF"	
elseif H64H== "7" then		
	A1 = "Album7GG"	
	A2 = "Album7GG"			
elseif H64H== "8" then		
	A1 = "Album8HH"	
	A2 = "Album8HH"			
elseif H64H== "9" then		
	A1 = "Album9II"	
	A2 = "Album9II"			
elseif H64H== "10" then			
	A1 = "Album10JJ"	
	A2 = "Album10JJ"				
	else
   A1 = "Album3CC"
  A2 = "Album3CC"
	end;

function CMTgif()
	if file_exists("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/A64A") == "OK" then;else;
file = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/A64A",1), "w"); file:write("0");file:close();usleep(100000);end;	
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/A64A",1), "rb"); local A64A = f:read("*all"); f:close(); usleep(100000);
if tonumber(A64A) == 0 then
		else;		
hashtagA = {'nice','cute','good','professional','super','hero','girl','boy','love','lovely','up','fly','sky','crazy','beautyful','pretty'}
hashtagA = hashtagA[math.random(1,#hashtagA)];usleep(100000);	
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.gif"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;	
tap(v[1]+math.random(1,10) , v[2]+math.random(1,5));usleep(500000);
inputText(hashtagA);usleep(2500000);	
tap(math.random(312,575) , math.random(630,790));usleep(2000000);	
gifOK = "0";for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.gifOK"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;gifOK = "1";usleep(2000000);end;	
if gifOK == "0" then;tap(math.random(30,200) , math.random(630,790));usleep(2000000);else;end;--if gifOK == "0"		
		end;--CMTPost.gif
	end;--if tonumber(A64A) == 0 then
end;--function CMTgif()

function CMTsticker()
		if file_exists("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/B64B") == "OK" then;else;

		else;

tap(v[1]+math.random(1,2) , v[2]+math.random(1,2));usleep(500000);

	RegionReactX = {130-math.random(5,60),320-math.random(5,60),500-math.random(5,60),690-math.random(5,60)};RegionReactX = RegionReactX[math.random(1, #RegionReactX)];usleep(100000) 
	RegionReactY = {math.random(950,1200),math.random(950,1200)};RegionReactY = RegionReactY[math.random(1, #RegionReactY)]; usleep(100000);      
    tap(RegionReactX, RegionReactY);usleep(500000);

		end;--CMTPost.StickerTrend

end;--function CMTsticker()

function rU()

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end

function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function CMTMediachoose()
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/H65H",1), "rb"); local H65H = f:read("*all"); f:close(); 
	
    if H65H == "1" then
	A1 = "Album1AA"
	A2 = "Album1AA"			
elseif H65H== "2" then		
	A1 = "Album2BB"	
	A2 = "Album2BB"			
elseif H65H== "3" then		
	A1 = "Album3CC"
	A2 = "Album3CC"
elseif H65H== "4" then		
	A1 = "Album4DD"	
	A2 = "Album4DD"
elseif H65H== "5" then		
	A1 = "Album5EE"	
	A2 = "Album5EE"	
elseif H65H== "6" then		
	A1 = "Album6FF"
	A2 = "Album6FF"	
elseif H65H== "7" then		
	A1 = "Album7GG"	
	A2 = "Album7GG"			
elseif H65H== "8" then		
	A1 = "Album8HH"	
	A2 = "Album8HH"			
elseif H65H== "9" then		
	A1 = "Album9II"	
	A2 = "Album9II"			
elseif H65H== "10" then			
	A1 = "Album10JJ"	
	A2 = "Album10JJ"				
	else
  A1 = "Album3CC"
  A2 = "Album3CC"
	end;

function CMTgif()
	if file_exists("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/A65A") == "OK" then;else;
file = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/A65A",1), "w"); file:write("0");file:close();end;--usleep(100000);end;	
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/A65A",1), "rb"); local A65A = f:read("*all"); f:close(); --usleep(100000);
if tonumber(A65A) == 0 then
		else;		
hashtagA = {'nice','cute','good','professional','super','hero','girl','boy','love','lovely','up','fly','sky','crazy','beautyful','pretty'}
hashtagA = hashtagA[math.random(1,#hashtagA)];usleep(100000);

		else;

	RegionReactX = {130-math.random(5,60),320-math.random(5,60),500-math.random(5,60),690-math.random(5,60)};RegionReactX = RegionReactX[math.random(1, #RegionReactX)];usleep(100000) 
	RegionReactY = {math.random(950,1200),math.random(950,1200)};RegionReactY = RegionReactY[math.random(1, #RegionReactY)]; usleep(100000);      
    tap(RegionReactX, RegionReactY);usleep(500000); 
StickerOK = "0";for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.StickerOK"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;StickerOK = "1";usleep(2000000);end;	
if StickerOK == "0" then;tap(RegionReactX, RegionReactY+30);usleep(2000000);else;end;--if gifOK == "0"						
		end;--CMTPost.StickerTrend	
		end;--CMTPost.Sticker

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

  function Sencmt()
	ot("CMTPost.Sendcmt",3);for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.Sendcmt"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;
   tap(v[1]+math.random(1,10) , v[2]+math.random(1,5));usleep(500000);
	CMTbtn = "1"					
   CMTOK = "1";usleep(2500000);	
	--=======================================================================================						
if CMTmedia == "1" then
ot("CMTPost.Media.posting",5);for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.Media.posting"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;--tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(300000)  
						--tap(v[1], v[2]);     usleep(math.random(1000000,1200000)); 
toast("wait for uploading...",10); usleep(2000000);	
ot("CMTPost.Media.justnow",30);for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.Media.justnow"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;--tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(300000)  
toast("upload video done..."); usleep(2000000)
			
	end;--CMTPost.Media.justnow
	end;--CMTPost.Media.posting
	else;end;--if CMTmedia == "1" then
		CMTmedia = "0"	
	--=======================================================================================
   end;--CMTPost.Sendcmt	
  end;--function Sencmt()

function MainfunctionCMTGroupX()

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function CMTMediachoose()
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/H66H",1), "rb"); local H66H = f:read("*all"); f:close();

    if H65H == "1" then

	A2 = "Album1AA"			
elseif H65H== "2" then		
	A1 = "Album2BB"	
	A2 = "Album2BB"			
elseif H65H== "3" then		
	A1 = "Album3CC"
	A2 = "Album3CC"
elseif H65H== "4" then		
	A1 = "Album4DD"	
	A2 = "Album4DD"
elseif H65H== "5" then		
	A1 = "Album5EE"	
	A2 = "Album5EE"	
elseif H65H== "6" then		
	A1 = "Album6FF"
	A2 = "Album6FF"	
elseif H65H== "7" then		
	A1 = "Album7GG"	
	A2 = "Album7GG"			
elseif H65H== "8" then		
	A1 = "Album8HH"	
	A2 = "Album8HH"			
elseif H65H== "9" then		
	A1 = "Album9II"	
	A2 = "Album9II"			
elseif H65H== "10" then			
	A1 = "Album10JJ"	
	A2 = "Album10JJ"				
	else
  A1 = "Album3CC"
  A2 = "Album3CC"
	end;

function CMTgif()
	if file_exists("/var/mobile/Library/AutoTouch/Scripts/.../.../temmp/A66A") == "OK" then;else;
file = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/A66A",1), "w"); file:write("0");file:close();end;--usleep(100000);end;	
local f = io.open(r(".../.../temmp/A66A",1), "rb"); local A66A = f:read("*all"); f:close(); --usleep(100000);
if tonumber(A66A) == 0 then
		else;		
hashtagA = {'nice','cute','good','professional','super','hero','girl','boy','love','lovely','up','fly','sky','crazy','beautyful','pretty'}
hashtagA = hashtagA[math.random(1,#hashtagA)];usleep(100000);	
for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.gif"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;	
tap(v[1]+math.random(1,10) , v[2]+math.random(1,5));usleep(500000);
inputText(hashtagA);usleep(2500000);	
tap(math.random(312,575) , math.random(630,790));usleep(2000000);	
gifOK = "0";for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.gifOK"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;gifOK = "1";usleep(2000000);end;	
if gifOK == "0" then;tap(math.random(30,200) , math.random(630,790));usleep(2000000);else;end;--if gifOK == "0"		
		end;--CMTPost.gif
	end;--if tonumber(A66A) == 0 then
end;--function CMTgif()

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end

function MainfunctionCMTGroup()	
			CMTbtn = "0"	
  function Sencmt()
	ot("CMTPost.Sendcmt",3);for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.Sendcmt"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;
   tap(v[1]+math.random(1,10) , v[2]+math.random(1,5));usleep(500000);
	CMTbtn = "1"					
   CMTOK = "1";usleep(2500000);	
	--=======================================================================================						
if CMTmedia == "1" then
ot("CMTPost.Media.posting",5);for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.Media.posting"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;--tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(300000)  
						--tap(v[1], v[2]);     usleep(math.random(1000000,1200000)); 
toast("wait for uploading...",10); usleep(2000000);	
ot("CMTPost.Media.justnow",30);for i, v in pairs(findImage(r("CMTPost.Media.justnow"), 1, 0.98, region, false)) do;--tap(v[1], v[2]);usleep(300000)  
toast("upload video done..."); usleep(2000000)
			
	end;--CMTPost.Media.justnow
	end;--CMTPost.Media.posting
		else;end;--if CMTmedia == "1" then
		CMTmedia = "0"	
	--=======================================================================================						
   end;--CMTPost.Sendcmt	
  end;--function Sencmt()
	
	
--CMTgif()    --CMTsticker()   --CMTiCon() --CMTtxt4only()   --CMTmedia4only()	--CMTtxt4Media()	
for rCMT = 1,math.random(1,6) do rAXX = math.random(1,5);usleep(100000);end;
	toast("type cmt is "..rAXX.."",20)
	if rAXX == 1 then
		CMTmedia = "0"
CMTOK = "0";CMTmedia4only();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);
	     if CMTOK == "1" then;else;CMTgif();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);end;	
         if CMTOK == "1" then;else;CMTsticker();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);end;			
         if CMTOK == "1" then;else;CMTiCon();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);end;		
         if CMTOK == "1" then;else;CMTtxt4only();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);end;			
         if CMTOK == "1" then;else;CMTtxt4Media();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);end;	
	elseif rAXX == 2 then
CMTOK = "0"; CMTsticker();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);	
		 if CMTOK == "1" then;else;CMTmedia4only();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);end;			
	     if CMTOK == "1" then;else;CMTgif();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);end;	
         if CMTOK == "1" then;else;CMTtxt4only();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);end;			
         if CMTOK == "1" then;else;CMTiCon();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);end;		
         if CMTOK == "1" then;else;CMTtxt4Media();usleep(100000);Sencmt();usleep(100000);end;

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do

UID = string.gsub(UIDX, " ", "")				
copyText(UID)

function tapInvite()
Invite = findColors({{16777215,0,0}, {16777215,0,9}, {16777215,0,18}, {16777215,8,6}, {16777215,8,19}, {16777215,18,9}, {16777215,19,18}, {16777215,30,19}, {16777215,25,6}, {16777215,35,5}, {16777215,42,0}, {16777215,41,6}, {16777215,42,19}, {16777215,51,3}, {16777215,55,19}, {16777215,51,9}, {16777215,60,12}, {16777215,71,11}, {16777215,66,6}, {16777215,66,19}, {1603570,66,9}, {1603570,66,16}, {1603570,29,7}, {1603570,4,12}}, 0, nil);
for i, v in pairs(Invite) do; toast("Invited")
	tap(v[1] + math.random(2,20), v[2]+ math.random(2,15));
		usleep(math.random(500000,1500000));
		break;end;--Invite
end;--function tapInvite()

function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]

function tapTick()
Tick = findColors({{6645611,0,0}, {6645611,8,-7}, {6645611,27,-8}, {6645611,35,1}, {6645611,35,18}, {6645611,26,27}, {6645611,9,27}, {6645611,1,18}, {16777215,10,18}, {16777215,29,-2}, {16777215,19,6}, {16777215,29,18}, {16777215,7,-1}}, 0, nil);
	for i, v in pairs(Tick) do; toast("Tick")
	tap(v[1] + math.random(2,10), v[2]+ math.random(2,5));
		usleep(math.random(2000000,3000000));
   InviteOK = "1"
	break;end;--Tick
end;--function tapTick()

local ColumeX2 = 2 -----none of set value--get colummn 2

local ColumeX4 = 4 -----none of set value--get colummn 4
function split(s, delimiter)
    result = {};
    for match in (s..delimiter):gmatch("(.-)"..delimiter) do
        table.insert(result, match);
    end
    return result;
end
local xxx=split(content, '\n')
local LineX = (xxx[LineInUIDfile])----local a = xxx[2]
copyText(LineX)	
function split(s, d)
    rtz = {};
    for m in (s..d):gmatch("(.-)"..d) do
        table.insert(rtz, m);
    end
    return rtz;
end
			
local a = LineX -----------------local a = xxx[2]
for i,v in pairs(split(a, '\n')) do
	local line = v
	local UID_PASS = split(v, '|')
--toast(''..UID_PASS[ColumeX1]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX2]..'-'..UID_PASS[ColumeX3]..'', 2)
	local UIDX = UID_PASS[1]
	local PassX = UID_PASS[2]
	local Code2FAX = UID_PASS[4]

function BRun()
	
	log("--=========================================================================================================");usleep(50000);
	log("--=========================================================================================================");usleep(50000);
	log("--=========================================================================================================");usleep(50000);

	if clipText() == nil or clipText() == "NO" or string.len(clipText()) > 2 then FrankyNouvaUpdate("ky");else;end;usleep(50000);

	if clipText() == nil or clipText() == "NO" or string.len(clipText()) > 2 then Netfix();usleep(10000000); FrankyNouvaUpdate("ky");else;end;usleep(50000);

	--===========================================================================================================
